"id":"QqZArcpHJxVj"},"source":["\n","**Цифра на определенном месте:**\n","\n","Последовательно записан натуральный ряд чисел.\n","\n","Какая цифра стоит в N позиции\n","\n","\n","Вввод:\n","\n","```\n","Введите номер позиции: 1234567890\n","```\n","\n","Вывод:\n","\n","```\n","8\n","```"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"id":"LwjYwBGcKiJ9","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1728400658628,"user_tz":-300,"elapsed":6523,"user":{"displayName":"Самоуел Емил","userId":"05889526955764185974"}},"outputId":"0eba92e5-d09b-46a5-9d1f-579d2174909d"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Введите номер позиции: 1234567890\n","Цифра на позиции  8\n"]}],"source":["def find_digit_at_position(n):\n","    length = 1\n","    count = 9\n","    start = 1\n","    while n > length * count:\n","        n -= length * count\n","        length += 1\n","        count *= 10\n","        start *= 10\n","    number = start + (n - 1) // length\n","    digit_index = (n - 1) % length\n","    return int(str(number)[digit_index])\n","n = int(input(\"Введите номер позиции: \"))\n","result = find_digit_at_position(n)\n","print(f\"Цифра на позиции  {result}\")\n"]}],"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[{"file_id":"1wk5ynY70nCt0ubANPIYZGhm_CIC3vPwo","timestamp":1728358661108},{"file_id":"1fct_CW6CXNQ7LoEF2ZJ4hoyr-wUtTlNk","timestamp":1728038946108}]},"kernelspec":{"display_name":"Python 3","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python"}},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":0}